text: Headhunterz (formerly known as Nasty D-Tuner) is Willem Rebergen, a Dutch hardstyle DJ and music producer. He gained his first major experience as a DJ at Defqon.1, a large hardstyle event in the Netherlands, where he was discovered by The Prophet. == References == *Official website *Headhunterz at Discogs.com *About Headhunterz *About Headhunterz on last.fm Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch DJs Category:Dutch record producers Category:Musicians from Utrecht (province)
